snippet.title: Outcast - A New Beginning | World Trailer
snippet.description:
This is Adelpha, home to the Talan people. The lush but dangerous planet is at risk of exploitation and destruction from an invading army.

The task at hand is dead serious - but that won’t stop Cutter from cracking some jokes... and skulls.

All footage captured in-engine.

Outcast - A New Beginning is coming soon to PC, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series S|X.
